process.name: Process Instance Summary Data by Application 2

processVariable.name: InstanceSummary
instancesStatuses
dataSeriesP

TWComponent.script: tw.local.sqlStatement select distinct application, name, value from ( SELECT lp1."NAME" application, LSW_BPD_STATUS_CODES."NAME" as name, count(LBI1.BPD_INSTANCE_ID) as value from LSW_BPD_INSTANCE LBI1, LSW_BPD_STATUS_CODES, lsw_project lp1 where LBI1.EXECUTION_STATUS(+) = LSW_BPD_STATUS_CODES.STATUS_ID and lp1.PROJECT_ID = LBI1.PROJECT_ID(+) and lp1.IS_TOOLKIT = 'F' and lp1.IS_SYSTEM = 'F' and 0 < (select count(lbw3.BPD_INSTANCE_ID) from lsw_bpd_instance lbw3, LSW_PROJECT lp3, LSW_BPD_STATUS_CODES lbsc3 where lbw3.EXECUTION_STATUS(+) = lbsc3.STATUS_ID and lp3.PROJECT_ID = lbw3.PROJECT_ID(+) and lp3.PROJECT_ID = lp1.PROJECT_ID and lbsc3.STATUS_ID in ('1','2','3','4','5','6')) group by lp1."NAME", LSW_BPD_STATUS_CODES."NAME" ) where value is not null order by name, application

tw.local.sqlStatement select distinct application, name, value from(SELECT lp1.NAME APPLICATION, LSW_BPD_STATUS_CODES.NAME as name, cast(count(LBI1.BPD_INSTANCE_ID) as char(20)) as value from LSW_BPD_STATUS_CODES LEFT OUTER JOIN LSW_BPD_INSTANCE LBI1 ON LBI1.EXECUTION_STATUS = LSW_BPD_STATUS_CODES.STATUS_ID, lsw_project lp1 LEFT OUTER JOIN LSW_BPD_INSTANCE LBI2 ON lp1.PROJECT_ID = LBI2.PROJECT_ID where lp1.IS_TOOLKIT = 'F' AND lp1.IS_SYSTEM = 'F' AND 0 <(select count(lbw3.BPD_INSTANCE_ID) from LSW_PROJECT lp3 LEFT OUTER JOIN lsw_bpd_instance lbw3 ON lp3.PROJECT_ID = lbw3.PROJECT_ID, LSW_BPD_STATUS_CODES lbsc3 LEFT OUTER JOIN lsw_bpd_instance lbw4 ON lbw4.EXECUTION_STATUS = lbsc3.STATUS_ID where lp3.PROJECT_ID = lp1.PROJECT_ID AND lbsc3.STATUS_ID in('1','2','3','4','5','6')) group by lp1.NAME,LSW_BPD_STATUS_CODES.NAME) where value is not null order by name,application

tw.local.sqlStatement select distinct application, name, value from(SELECT lp1.NAME application, LSW_BPD_STATUS_CODES.NAME as name, cast(count(LBI1.BPD_INSTANCE_ID) as varchar(20)) as value from LSW_BPD_STATUS_CODES LEFT OUTER JOIN LSW_BPD_INSTANCE LBI1 ON LBI1.EXECUTION_STATUS = LSW_BPD_STATUS_CODES.STATUS_ID RIGHT OUTER JOIN lsw_project lp1 ON lp1.PROJECT_ID = LBI1.PROJECT_ID where lp1.IS_TOOLKIT = 'F' AND lp1.IS_SYSTEM = 'F' AND 0 <(select count(lbw3.BPD_INSTANCE_ID) from LSW_PROJECT lp3 LEFT OUTER JOIN lsw_bpd_instance lbw3 ON lp3.PROJECT_ID = lbw3.PROJECT_ID RIGHT OUTER JOIN LSW_BPD_STATUS_CODES lbsc3 ON lbw3.EXECUTION_STATUS = lbsc3.STATUS_ID where lp3.PROJECT_ID = lp1.PROJECT_ID AND lbsc3.STATUS_ID in('1','2','3','4','5','6')) group by lp1.NAME,LSW_BPD_STATUS_CODES.NAME) AS TabAl where value is not null order by name,application
